The woven cotton blend that’s both and moisture-wicking helps to regulate your body on and off your board. Our special construction offers unrestricted movement specifically designed for skateboarding. A 1.75” waist and a non-restrictive front pouch, these RDS boxers will keep your stuff feeling comfy all day long!
tags: Bottoms, Boxers, MBottoms, mens, SP23

title: RDS X CAB JACKET
body_html:
The Red Dragons are once again proud to collaborate with the legendary Steve Caballero on this latest RDS windbreaker.  This lightweight breathable RDS jacket will keep you skating through the fall and winter as it’s equipped with a Diamond Mesh Lining to lock in the heat, and an outer Nylon Shell to help protect against the elements. 

"Super stoked to be part of the RDS crew who I've admired for years. It's always year of the Dragon!" - Steve Caballer
tags: HD22, Jackets, mens, MTops, NewHD22, SM22, Tops
